</li>
</ul><h3>Content Prereqs</h3><aside class="admonition note"><p class="admonition-title">Note</p><p class="admonition-title">Functional Analysis and Dirac Notation</p><p>No prior familiarity with operators, Dirac notation, Hilbert spaces, functional analysis, or the application of operators within quantum mechanics is assumed for this lesson.</p></aside><h2>Resources</h2><h3>Related Lessons</h3><ul>
